Make `CompositionGraph` the authoritative projection for shader/reference facts and contribution-index lookups, while preserving legacy timeline and contribution-index inputs as compatibility sources. This is a bridge toward the North Star, not a contradiction: M1b intentionally narrows graph authority to shader/ref facts, contribution refs, and `consumes` edges, while leaving target paths, live/agent material promotion, process vocabularies, output-format vocabularies, and future edge kinds out of scope.

